{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1>how to disable rule</h1>\n<h2>全局修改</h2>\n<p>在eslint 配置文件中的rules中修改</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-json line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-json\">  rules<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"promise/param-names\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">\"off\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h2>局部修改</h2>\n<p>通过注释来设置 (可以设在函数定义上 作用范围为整个函数))</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-js line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* eslint prefer-promise-reject-errors: \"off\" */</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/cube/eslint/"}}